      <h3 class="title">Flowing Pandaren Spirit - Dread Waste (61.5, 87.6)</h3>
      <div class="story">
        <p>In this fight I have always use a Dread Hatchling and a Crow to win.
          However, I have heard about a Idol build. Therefore I might change this page if it is
          better.  This strat has about an 80% chance to change.
          If this strat is not good for you there is a
          Wowhead link at the bottom, so you cant comb through the other strats.
        </p>
        <h4 class="title">The Pets</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Dread Hatchling (1,1,1)</li>
          <li>Crow (1,2,2)</li>
          <li>Carry</li>

          <p>This fight has some AOE so you need a mid-level pet for this fight. I tend to
          use the same pet from the Farmer Nishi fight.</p>
          <p>Pet will be level 19 without a food buff.</p>
        </ul>
        <h4 class="title">The Strat</h4>
        <br />
        <h6 class="title">Marley</h6>
        <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Nocturnal Strike - If you miss just reset the fight</li>
          <li>Call Darkness - This will miss but you change the weather.</li>
          <li>Peck to win</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <h6 class="title">Tiptoe</h6>
        <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Nocturnal Strike - 100% hit now because of the weather :D</li>
          <li>Peck till Dread dies</li>
          <li>Swap in Crow</li>
          <li>Call Darkness to win</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <h6 class="title">Pandaren Water Spirit</h6>
        <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Swap to carry</li>
          <li>Swap back</li>
          <li>Peck to win you can use the
            Strike but it is at 50% because this pet is immune to weather
          </li>
        </ul>
        </p>
      </div>
